item.title: CVE-2023-41256|2023-09-11T18:55:05.231Z -- dover%20fueling%20solutions -- maglink%20lx%20web%20console%20configuration
item.description: Dover Fueling Solutions MAGLINK LX Web Console Configuration versions 2.5.1, 2.5.2, 2.5.3, 2.6.1, 2.11, 3.0, 3.2, and 3.3 are vulnerable to authentication bypass that could allow an unauthorized attacker to obtain user access.
